{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"496abc8e6e","title":"如傅作义南逃华北第一兵团三个纵队应到石家庄堵击","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f4de46891d","index":0,"year":1948,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"496abc8e6e"}],"tags":[{"id":"8ea55d34c1","name":"胡耀邦","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d6ce594f84","type":"paragraph","text":"如傅作义南逃华北第一兵团三个纵队应到石家庄堵击口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"496abc8e6e"},{"id":"f66205aeb7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年12月27日）周、陈、胡感十时电器。（一）假如傅军向南突围（现时尚未确定），你们率三个纵队以五天行程赶到石家庄为最好。（二）八、十三、十五的人数及训练情形如何，留下八个旅假如不能保守输次及东山各要点，则应在不能保守准备暂时放弃之，是否对于以后攻城极为不利，望告。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"496abc8e6e"},{"id":"05afa4bd7f","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"496abc8e6e"},{"id":"55a289fd4a","type":"paragraph","text":"二十七日二十时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华北军区第一兵团副司令员兼副政治委员周士第、参长陈漫远和政治部主任胡耀邦的电报。[2]指1948年12月27日10时周士第、陈爱远、胡耀邦给中共中央军家庄。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"496abc8e6e"}],"page":{"id":"fdee733d2f","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"496abc8e6e","start":463,"end":463}}}},"__N_SSG":true}